description: During execution, [Threat Group-3390](https://attack.mitre.org/groups/G0027) malware deobfuscates and decompresses code that was encoded with Metasploit’s shikata_ga_nai encoder as well as compressed with LZNT1 compression.(Citation: Securelist LuckyMouse June 2018)
